{"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItem","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OUDSCheckboxItem","symbolKind":"struct","roleHeading":"Structure","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents16OUDSCheckboxItemV","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItem","kind":"identifier"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItem","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"Layouts","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Layouts"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"reversed"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing checkbox indicator and a leading optional image"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Indicator states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you are looking for a checkbox component with three states, use instead "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"anchor":"Particular-cases","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Particular cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as disabled.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image."}]},{"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom checkbox trait.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Forbidden by design"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\")","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Bazinga!\", helper: \"Doll-Dagga Buzz-Buzz Ziggety-Zag\")","","    \/\/ A trailing checkbox with a label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn,","                     label: \"We live in a fabled world\",","                     helper: \"Of dreaming boys and wide-eyed girls\",","                     isReversed: true,","                     icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $isOn, label: \"Hello world\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to manage the RTL mode quite easily and switch your layouts (flip image, indicator in RTL leading i.e. in the right):"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSCheckboxItem(isOn: $selection,","                     labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                     icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                     flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                     isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Suggestions","anchor":"Suggestions"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/09d860-checkbox\/t\/14bf4bd854","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/09d860-checkbox"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.1.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"name":"Version","type":"aside","style":"note"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Since","type":"aside","style":"note"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some checkboxes components with labels and icons."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a checkbox with only an indicator prefer instead "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitem"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponent